r your video recording.</p> <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Record/General" class="btn btn-primary">More</a></div></div><div class="card card-inverse shadow mb" style="background-color: #333; border-color: #333;"> <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/images/Image041_small.png" alt="InstarVision 2.0 :: Layout"><div class="card-block"><h4 class="card-title">Schedule</h4><p class="card-text">Program regular video recording for your cameras.</p> <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Record/Schedule" class="btn btn-primary">More</a></div></div><div class="card card-inverse shadow mb" style="background-color: #333; border-color: #333;"> <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/images/Image042_small.png" alt="InstarVision 2.0 :: Layout"><div class="card-block"><h4 class="card-title">Alarm</h4><p class="card-text">Activate motion detection and alarm recordings.</p> <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Record/Alarm" class="btn btn-primary">More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="card-deck-wrapper"><div class="card-deck"><div class="card card-inverse shadow mb" style="background-color: #333; border-color: #333;"> <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/images/Image044_small.png" alt="InstarVision 2.0 :: Layout"><div class="card-block"><h4 class="card-title">Photoseries</h4><p class="card-text">Set up an automated snapshot recording.</p> <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Record/Photoseries" class="btn btn-primary">More</a></div></div><div class="card card-inverse shadow mb" style="background-color: #333; border-color: #333;"> <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/images/Image045-1_small.png" alt="InstarVision 2.0 :: Layout"><div class="card-block"><h4 class="card-title">Email</h4><p class="card-text">Let InstarVision notify you with alarm emails.</p> <a href="/Software/Windows/InstarVision/Record/Email" class="btn btn-primary">More</a></div></div><div class="card card-inverse shadow mb" style="background-color: #333; border-color: #333;"> <im